      "textArabic": "قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ",
      "textTransliteration": "Qul aAAoothu birabbi alnnasi",
      "textEnglishSaheeh": "Say, \"I seek refuge in the Lord of mankind,",
      "textEnglishMustafa": "Say, ˹O Prophet,˺ “I seek refuge in the Lord of humankind,",
      "juz": 30,
